{
  "stem": "24409.12",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "After four years there, I was transferred to Germany.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I was in charge of psychology for 1,000 air commanders.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Was ?] [? there ?] [? a ?] [? whole ?] [INAUDIBLE] of Americans there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And there, I made my living by being in the Army.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "The Army pays quite well.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And then I got out and became chief psychologist for the District of Columbia for the welfare system.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They had-- the District of Columbia had-- their-- all juvenile delinquents were committed to the District of Columbia.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They were committed to the Children's Center.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And-- and I was in charge of this.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And after 10 years, I was [INAUDIBLE] area.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I left the civil service and became consultant for a year to the-- in delinquency for the government of the state of Nebraska, which was that I worked during the week there.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And on the weekends, I always flew back.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "It was-- I could fly as a retired-- as a military reservist, I would fly militarily.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And there was a plane going every day, every week.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "On Friday, it left from-- the Air Force base.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "There was a big Air Force base there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And it was-- it was not in Nebraska.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "It was in Kansas, to-- to-- to-- Offutt-- Offutt Air Force Base, through here to Andrews.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And then Sunday evening, I flew back to [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I spent every weekend here.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And after a year, I-- my report was completed there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I went into private practice.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now-- now in between, I had been sent in Germany, from '55 to '58.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there, too, complete therapeutic training in both the Freudian method-- in all three, the Freudian method, the Adlerian method, and the Jungian method, which was unusual.",
      "word_count": 27
    }
  ],
